quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Haa, miim."
  43,2,"Mi woo…óndirii defere …ďanngunde ndeen !"
  43,3,"Min ma…óii nde janngeteende [e …óemngal] aarabu, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  43,4,"Pellet, hende woni ka Amen gaa, ka yumma defte, toownde, √Īe√Īaande."
  43,5,"E Min ngacciray njippinangol on jantoore ndeen, …óuurngal on, fii on ngonii yim…ďe fantin…ďe?"
  43,6,"∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ďe …ďe Min nuli e adinoo…ďe …ďeen."
  43,7,"Annabaajo araali e ma…ď…ďe, si wonaa …ďe njalkitay mo."
  43,8,"Min kalki ko …ďuri …ďe sa…ótude doole ! Toode mise adinoo…ďe …ďeen jawtiino."
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe: ""Ko hommbo tagi kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin?"" ∆Āe mbi'ay: ""Ko poolu…óo, ganndu…óo on tagi …óii""."
  43,10,"Oon mba…óiran…óo on leydi ndin weertaandi, O wa…óani on …óate e mayri, fii no …óoworon."
  43,11,"Oon jippinr…óo to…ďo ka kammuu, yeru haaju, Min nguurnitiri ngo leydi maayndi. Ko noon yaltinirte…óon."
  43,12,"On tak…óo nooneeji …óin fow, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óiin, ko mba…ó…óoron,"
  43,13,"fii yo on potondir e hoore majji, refti ngannditon neema Joomi mon on, tuma potondir…óon e majji, mb'on on tuma: ""Senaare woodanii eeltan…óo min …óuum On, min ngonaano taaqanaa…ďe …óum."
  43,14,"minen noon, ko ka Joomi amen woni ko min nduttotoo""."
  43,15,"∆Āe mba…óani mo ge…óal e jiyaa…ďe Makko …ďeen ! Pellet, on ne…ó…óaŇčke ko jeddu…óo …ďanngu…óo."
  43,16,"Kaa woo O jogiti …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen?"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ď…ďe wewliniraama ko o wa…óirani kon Hinaranke On misal, ye'eso makko ngon ni…ď…ďita metteendi hombo suu…ói."
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kaŇčko on ka yeddondiral, wonaa o …ďannginoowo haala?"
  43,19,"∆Āe mba…ói Malaa'ikaa…ďe taw…ďe …ďeen ko jiyaa…ďe Joom yurmeende oon, rew…ďe ! Kere …ďe seedino tageede …ďeen? Awa fii seedagol ma…ď…ďe ngol winndete, …ďe lamnditoyee."
  43,20,"∆Āe mbi'iti: ""Si Joom yurmeende On haajuno, min ndewataano …ďe"". ∆Āe alanaa …óuum hay e ganndal; …ďe ngonaani, si wonaa hi…ďe pena."
  43,21,"Kaa ko defftere Min ngaddani …ďe ado ndee …óoo, hara ko nden woni ko …ďe njogitii?"
  43,22,"Si ko woni, …ďe mbi'iu: ""Minen Min tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďeen e diina, haray ko e batteeji ma…ď…ďe min peewirta""."
  43,23,"Ko wano non, Min nulaali jeertinoowo aditaade ma e saare woo, si wonaa hooree…ďe ma…ď…ďe neemii…ďe mbi'ay: ""Minen Min tawu baabiraa…ďe amen …ďen e diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ď…ďe …óin men √Īermtinta""."
  43,24,"O maaki: ""Hay si mi addan on ko …ďuri feewude kon ko tawru…óon baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen?"" ∆Āe mbi'i: ""Minen dey, ko min jeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon e mum koon""."
  43,25,"Min njottii e ma…ď…ďe. ndaare no battande fennu…ďe …ďeen mba'unoo."
  43,26,"JaŇčto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo been makko e yim…ďe makko …ďeen: ""Min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e kon ko ndewoton,"
  43,27,"si wanaa On tak…óo lam, KaŇčko oon, O feewnay kam""."
  43,28,"O wa…ói ngool konngol heddotoongol …ďaawo makko, mbelajo'o, …ďe nduttoto."
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii …ďee …óoo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, haa nde goonga kan ngarnoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo."
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe mbi'i: ""∆äuum ko mbilewu, minen ko min njeddu…ďe …óuum""."
  43,31,"∆Āe mb'iti: ""Ko ha…óno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko maw…óo ca'e …óen …ói…ói?"""
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen? Awa ko Minen ngoni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óiin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Min …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa ndeen, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e ko ko …ďe moo…ďata."
  43,33,"Si wonaano fii wata yim…ďe …ďeen ngon mofte goote, Min mba…óayno e cuu…ói kala jeddu…óo Hinnaranke Oon: ki…ď…ďe kaalisi e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra;"
  43,34,"(Min mba…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óiin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo,"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óuum fow wonaani, si wonaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko La'akara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e jaŇčtoore Hinaranko On, Min nguurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata."
  43,37,"∆äiin (awaseeji) noon, ko sakkoray…ói …ďe e peewal ngal, haa ka …ďe cikkata hi…ďe peewi."
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amin, o wi'a: ""Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal pu…ó…óir…óe …óen …ói…ói wo…ó…óiri ! A bonii cinndadii…óo !""."
  43,39,"[∆äuum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√Īii - won'de ko ka lepte kaawtu…óon."
  43,40,"E ko an naninta paa…óu…óo maa feewnaa bun…óo e on won…óo e ndeer majjere …ďanngunde?"
  43,41,"Si Min ngar ∆īettitude ma, ko Min yo…ďottotoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe."
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Min kammbirani …ďeen kon, haray noon ko Min gaynoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe."
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maa…óa. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol pocciingol."
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yim…ďe maa …ďeen. Aray nde la…ďnditee…óon."
  43,45,"Lamndii e …ďeen Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďe Min nulunoo ado maa, si Min mba…óuno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, dewetee…ói goo?"
  43,46,"GooŇč…óii Min immindinii Muusaa e aayeeje Amen …óeen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: ""Ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tagoore""."
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ďe aayeeje Amen …óren, e jaka yoo hi…ďe njala…ói."
  43,48,"Min hollaali …ďe aaya, si wonaa haray on …ďuri adii…óo mo on mawnude. Min nanngiri …ďe lepte …óeen, mbelajo'o, …ďe nduttoto."
  43,49,"∆Āe mbi'i: ""Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano min Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maa…óa. Pellet, ko min feewoo…ďe""."
  43,50,"Nde Min huncannoo…ďe lepte …óeen, e jaka yoo, hi…ďe pirta [ahadi]."
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yim…ďe …ďeen, o wi'i: ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, wanaa miin jey laamu Misra? E hino …óii can…ói no ila e ley ku…ďeeji am? E on nji'ataa?"
  43,52,"Kaa mi …ďuraa teddude oo koy…óo mo e…ď…ďataa la…ď…ďinnde haala?"
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawe kaŇčŇče mbrnee e makko? Ma Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri?"""
  43,54,"O …óaytini yim…ďe makko …ďen, …ďe …óowtii mo. Pellet, …ďeen …óon laatino yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe."
  43,55,"Nde …ďe tikkinnoo Min, Min yottii e ma…ď…ďe; Min njooli …ďe fof."
  43,56,"Min mba…ói …ďe ardii…ďe e yeru, wonan'de sakkiitii…ďe …ďeen."
  43,57,"Tuma nde ge…óal neene Maryama on piyiranoo misal, tawaa yoo, yim…ďe maa …ďeen no soo∆īira …óuum."
  43,58,"…ďe mbi'i: ""Ko dewetee…ói amen …óin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude, kaa ko KaŇčko?"" ∆Āe piyiranaali ma ngal (misal), si wonaa fii wennjugol. Wurin, ko …ďe yim…ďe sa…ótu…ďe mbe√Īe."
  43,59,"Awa (Iisaa) wonaani, si wanaa jiyaa…óo mo Min neemini e mum, Min mba…ói mo yeru wonan'de …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďeen."
  43,60,"Si Moen kaajuno, Min wa…ótitirayno on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo ka leydi."
  43,61,"Pellet non, ko o anndinorde Darngal. Wota on cikkito fii maggal. Jokkee kam, ko …óuum woni laawol Pocciingol ngol."
  43,62,"Wota seytaane falo on ! tawde pellet, ko o ga√Īo mon …ďanngu…óo."
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa ardunoo e …ďanngu…ói …óin, o maaki: ""GooŇč…óii mi ardanii on e √Īee√Īal, e no mi …ďannginirana on yoga e ko luutondir…óon e muu…óum. Haray kulee Allah, …óofto…óon mi."
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Alla Woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Ndewee Mo. Ko …óuum woni laawol pocciingol ngol""."
  43,65,"Feddeeji …óiin luutondiri hakkunde majji. Bone woodanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, immorde e lepte √Īalaande mu'usuu…óe !"
  43,66,"Hara …ďe habbi si wpnaa nde Darngal ngal ardata …ďe e juhal, hara …ďe so'aa anndude?"
  43,67,"Weldu…ďe …ďeen, nden √Īalnde, yoga ma…ď…ďe ko ayroo…ďe yoga; si wonaa gooŇč…óui…ďe …ďeen."
  43,68,"Ko onon yo jiyaa…ďe Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde; wonaa on sunotoo…ďe kadi."
  43,69,"…ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óeen, …ďe ngoni jebbilii…ďe,"
  43,70,"naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nanndu…ďe e mon, ho…óon sa…ónee""."
  43,71,"[Golloo…ďe] hino wannginee e ma…ď…ďe, mirannji kaŇčŇče e yeddu…óe; hino ton kadi: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitoo. Hara le, ko on duumotoo…ďe toon."
  43,72,"Ko on ngoni Aljanna mo roninira…óon, sabu ko ko ngollayno…óon."
  43,73,"Hino woodani on toon, muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói, …ói √Īaamoton e mum."
  43,74,"Pellet, bon…ďe …ďen, ko ka lepte Jahannama …ďe luttoyta,"
  43,75,"…ďe koynantaake, tee hara ko …ďe ta∆īii…ďe toon."
  43,76,"Min too√Īaani …ďe few, si ko woni, ko kam…ďe woni too√Īu…ďe …ďeen."
  43,77,"∆Āe nodda: ""Ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen !"" O wi'i: ""Pellet, ko on luttoo…ďe [toon] !"""
  43,78,"""GooŇč…óii Min ngaddanii on goonga kan ; kono …óuu…óu…ďe e mon, ko a√Ī…ďe goonga""."
  43,79,"Kaa …ďe e…ď…ďu fehre ? Doo ko Min fewjoo…ďe !"
  43,80,"Maa hara …ďe cikku Min nanataa gunndooji ma…ď…ďe e sirru ma…ď…ďe? Oo‚Äôowoye! Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďeen hino maandina takko ma…ď…ďe."
  43,81,"Maaku: ""Si Hinaranko on no njogitii …ďi…ó…óo, ko miin adotonoo rewude oon""."
  43,82,"Senaare woodanii Jey…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin, Jey…óo Arsi kin; laa…ďu…óo e kon ko …ďe cifrotta mo."
  43,83,"Accu…ďe …ďe jumpa, …ďe pija haa …ďe hawroya e √Īalaande ma…ď…ďe nde…ďe fodaa."
  43,84,"Ko KaŇčko woni On dewetee…óo ka kammu e dewetee…óo ka leydi, ko KaŇčko kadi woni √Ďee√Īo, ganndu…óo On."
  43,85,"Barke heewanii on mo woodani …óum, laamu kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka makko anndal fii Darngal woni. Ko ka makko kadi nduttete…óon."
  43,86,"∆äi …ďe ndewata …óin ga makko jeyah tefoore, si wonaa seedii…ďe goonga …ďeen, hara he…ďe nganndi."
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ďe, ko hommbo woni ko tagi …ďe? ∆Āe mbi'ay: ""Ko Allah"". Ko holno non …ďe njiiliraa?"
  43,88,"[Himo anndi kadi] fii ko (Nulaa…óo) oon maakunoo kon: ""Ko an yo Joomi, pellet, …ďee ko yim…ďe …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa""."
  43,89,"Yaafo …ďe, maakaa: ""Kisal !"" Aray ndebe ngannda."
